{
  "texts": [
    "Extensive testing on various tasks validates its robustness across different applications.",
    "We evaluate it in the LLM-based federated fine-tuning setting to further investigate its effectiveness.Optimization on Both Sides.",
    "We also evaluate the performance of FedOPT [70], which performs adaptive optimization on both the client side and server side.",
    "FedOPT employs adaptive optimization methods on the server and clients for faster convergence compared to traditional methods, robust to noisy gradients, and provides theoretical convergence guarantees that ensure reliable performance across scenarios.",
    "We evaluate FedOPT as another type of federated algorithm to assess its performance in comparison to other types of algorithms.Personalized Learning."
  ]
}